items.title: Bryant's HR, 4 RBIs send Cubs past Mets
items.summary: If the Cubs are going to repeat as National League Central champs, they need Kris Bryant, and he hit his first home run of September, a three-run shot in the fourth inning, and 26th of the season to spark an 8-3 victory over the Mets on Tuesday night.
